&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.reddit.com/r/typescript/comments/ihpnme/opinion_on_explicit_return_types/&#34;&gt;Reddit Thread Where The Majority Support Return Types&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://topher.io/writing/make-returns-explicit&#34;&gt;Make Returns Explicit&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
